{
  "texts": [
    "10 proposed BSN-Care, a contemporary healthcare system, for Remote Patient Monitoring (RPM).",
    "The BSN-Care architecture incorporates traditional devices such as BSN (Body Sensor Network), Local Processing Unit (LPU), and BSN-Care Server.",
    "The BSN-Care Server utilizes a heuristic technique to interpret patient physiological data transmitted via the LPU in the BSN-Care system.",
    "If the physiological data surpasses predetermined criteria, the BSN-Care Server sends an alert to healthcare providers.",
    "Dwivedi et al."
  ]
}